    List View for Blog Posts:
    Fetch a list of all blog posts.

    Detail View for Blog Posts:
    Retrieve the details of a specific blog post.

    Create View for Blog Posts:
    Create a new blog post.

    Update View for Blog Posts:
    Update an existing blog post.

    Delete View for Blog Posts:
    Delete an existing blog post.

    List View for Post Reviews:
    Fetch a list of reviews/comments for a specific blog post.

    Create View for Post Reviews:
    Add a new review/comment to a blog post.

    Update View for Post Reviews:
    Update an existing review/comment for a blog post.

    Delete View for Post Reviews:
    Delete a review/comment for a blog post.

    User Activity History View:
    Display a user's activity history, such as their post creation and review activity.